Package: bytecli
Version: 1.1.6
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-4.0, gir1.2-adw-1,
         python3-dbus, xclip, xdotool, x11-utils, libportaudio2, python3-numpy,
         python3-pip, python3-xlib, wmctrl
Description: Local voice dictation for Linux, powered by local ASR models
 Press Alt to record, release to transcribe and paste.
 Runs entirely offline using SenseVoice, Fun-ASR-Nano, Qwen3-ASR,
 faster-whisper, GLM-ASR evaluation support, and OpenAI Whisper fallback.
 Features a floating indicator pill, dark GTK 4 settings panel,
 and bilingual (English/Chinese) support.
Maintainer: ByteCLI <noreply@github.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/StriderXOXO/byteCLI
